<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10468325>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Pyrops clavatus (Westwood, 1839), ♁, Chiang Rai Province, Wiang Pa Pao District, Mae Chedi, 2.VI.2021 (THN- HM). (A) Habitus, dorsal view; (B) habitus, ventral view; (C) habitus, lateral view; (D) head and thorax, dorsal view; (E) head, perpendicular view of frons." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10468325/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10468329>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Pyrops condorinus (Lallemand, 1960), ♁, Chonburi Province, Chanta Ten Waterfall, 7.VII.2022 (RBMF). (A) ha- bitus, dorsal view; (B) habitus, ventral view; (C) habitus, lateral view; (D) head and thorax, dorsal view; (E) head, perpendicular view of frons." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10468329/files/figure.png" ;
